{"cardlistInfo":{"v_p":6,"containerid":"100303type=555&q=韶关&t=0","title_top":"搜索","title":"","total":0,"show_style":1,"buttons":[],"actionlog":"","can_shared":0,"shared_text":"","shared_text_qrcode":"","cardlist_title":"","desc":"","page_type":"03","filter_group":"","background":"","cardlist_menus":[{"type":"button_menus_refresh","name":"刷新"},{"type":"gohome","name":"返回首页","params":{"scheme":"sinaweibo:\/\/gotohome"}}]},"cards":[{"card_type":11,"card_type_name":"","card_id":"bag_group","title":"","scheme":"sinaweibo:\/\/cardlist?containerid=2310360030_8008644030000000000_%E9%9F%B6%E5%85%B3_1_8008644020000000000&needlocation=1","card_group":[{"card_type":8,"card_type_name":"","card_id":"search_0","title":"","scheme":"sinaweibo:\/\/cardlist?containerid=2310360030_8008644030000000000_%E9%9F%B6%E5%85%B3_1_8008644020000000000&needlocation=1","pic":"http:\/\/ww2.sinaimg.cn\/wap180\/4e704b16jw1esr3h0zfutj20ci0ciq64.jpg","title_sub":"韶关","desc1":"韶关，简称“韶”，古称韶州，得名于丹霞的名山韶石山，取韶石之名。韶州得名韶关始于明清之际，在今韶关市区先后设立水陆三个税关收税，俗称韶关。位于广东省北部，北界湖南，东邻江西，东南面、南面和西面分别与本省河源、惠州、广州及清远等市接壤。素有“三省通衢”之称。  韶关地形以山地丘陵为主，仁化县丹霞山一带以独特的红岩地貌闻名于世，是中国典型的“丹霞地貌”所在地和命名地， 面积1.85万平方公里，辖浈江区、武江区、曲江区、仁化县、始兴县、翁源县、新丰县和乳源瑶族自治县，代管乐昌市和南雄市， 2013年末户籍人口为345.93万。  韶关市是广东省历史文化名城，还是广东省规划建设的粤北区域性中心城市和韶关都市区的核心城市，是全国交通枢纽城市之一。  地处粤北，外接湘赣，内联珠三角，自古是中国南方的交通要冲，素有广东的北大门之称， 是华北及长江中下游地区与华南沿海之间最重要的陆上通道和关口，粤湘赣交界地区商品集散中心。韶关拥有丰富的土地资源、森林资源、矿产资源，有着“华南生物基因库”、“岭南名郡”、“中国锌都”，“有色金属之乡”，国家园林城市等美誉。 ","desc2":"","title_flag_pic":"","source":"","card_display_type":1,"display_arrow":1,"buttons":[],"is_asyn":0,"right_pannel":[],"actionlog":{"act_code":695,"luicode":"","uicode":"10000495","fid":"102803_2222","ext":"near:Yiqing_search_business"},"openurl":""}],"buttontitle":"","display_arrow":1,"show_type":0,"openurl":"","is_asyn":0},{"card_type":11,"card_type_name":"以下是“韶关”相关地点","card_id":"search_poilist","title":"以下是“韶关”相关地点","scheme":"sinaweibo:\/\/cardlist?containerid=2306570042B2094652DA6FA5FE419D","card_group":[{"card_type":8,"card_type_name":"","card_id":"search_1","title":"","scheme":"sinaweibo:\/\/cardlist?containerid=2306570042B2094652DA68A6FB429C","pic":"http:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/4e704b16jw1e2nz9wsm4qj.jpg","title_sub":"韶关丹霞山和景温泉","desc1":"1.1万人去过·韶关市仁化县丹霞山新山门外和景酒店","desc2":"","title_flag_pic":"","source":"","card_display_type":1,"display_arrow":0,"buttons":[{"pic":"https:\/\/h5.sinaimg.cn\/upload\/100\/972\/2020\/12\/04\/chakan.png","type":"link","name":"查看","params":{"scheme":"sinaweibo:\/\/cardlist?containerid=2306570042B2094652DA68A6FB429C","actionlog":{"act_code":695,"luicode":"","uicode":"10000495","fid":"102803_2222","ext":"near:Yiqing_search_poi"}}}],"is_asyn":0,"right_pannel":[],"actionlog":{"act_code":695,"luicode":"","uicode":"10000495","fid":"102803_2222","ext":"near:Yiqing_search_poi"},"openurl":""},{"card_type":8,"card_type_name":"","card_id":"search_2","title":"","scheme":"sinaweibo:\/\/cardlist?containerid=2306570042B2094757D06FA4FA419A","pic":"http:\/\/ww3.sinaimg.cn\/wap180\/4e704b16jw1e8bto1vb6rj2096096wet.jpg","title_sub":"韶关东站","desc1":"1.1万人去过·广东省韶关市北江路
